  "intent": "Perform a bead-based ELISA assay across 12 columns using magnetic separation. Add 20\u00b5L capture beads to samples, incubate with shaking at 1000rpm for 60 minutes, then wash 3 times with 250\u00b5L wash buffer. Add 100\u00b5L HRP-conjugated detection antibody, incubate for 60 minutes with shaking, wash 3 times. Add 100\u00b5L substrate solution, incubate for 5 minutes, then add 50\u00b5L stop solution. Transfer final 100\u00b5L supernatant to reading plate for optical density measurement.",
